<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 00:30:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“以色列当权者正在武装他们的支持者。政治影响是深远的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/people-in-power-in-israel-are-arming-supporters-the-political-implications-are-profound/0000018d-8ade-d5e7-ad8d-ebfe637e0000</link><description>他曾经将以色列视为安全使用枪支的典范。现在，美国枪支政策专家警告以色列正在犯与美国相同的错误</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 00:08:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/people-in-power-in-israel-are-arming-supporters-the-political-implications-are-profound/0000018d-8ade-d5e7-ad8d-ebfe637e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的生育率正在进入一个引人注目的新时代</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-fertility-rate-is-entering-a-dramatic-new-era/0000018d-8a6b-d9cc-a5cd-fffb664b0000</link><description>以色列各族群中的女性生育的孩子越来越少。世俗社会正危险地徘徊在所谓的更替水平附近，此时他们的数量开始萎缩</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 22:36:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israels-fertility-rate-is-entering-a-dramatic-new-era/0000018d-8a6b-d9cc-a5cd-fffb664b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁讨论哈马斯停火提议，抗议人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/protests-held-for-against-hostage-deal-as-war-cabinet-discusses-hamas-proposal/0000018d-8a7a-d9cc-a5cd-fffa554c0000</link><description>数千人在耶路撒冷的以色列政府大院外示威反对释放人质协议，而在特拉维夫，人质的家人及其支持者则抗议支持协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 21:41:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/protests-held-for-against-hostage-deal-as-war-cabinet-discusses-hamas-proposal/0000018d-8a7a-d9cc-a5cd-fffa554c0000</guid></item><item><title>延长以色列兵役期限的法案因豁免正统派而引起愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/bill-extending-israeli-army-service-draws-ire-for-exempting-haredim/0000018d-8a40-d443-a19f-fed132dc0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，该计划旨在满足10月7日事件以及加沙地带战争后果后的军队建设需求，但没有提及征召极端正统派人员的问题</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/bill-extending-israeli-army-service-draws-ire-for-exempting-haredim/0000018d-8a40-d443-a19f-fed132dc0000</guid></item><item><title>当动物饲料制成的皮塔饼是您最好的情况时：加沙地带北部的生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/when-pita-made-of-animal-feed-is-your-best-case-scenario-life-in-northern-gaza/0000018d-89f5-d5e7-ad8d-ebf59baf0000</link><description>没有香烟、电或饮用水；一罐金枪鱼售价 100 谢克尔，但 ATM 机被关闭：加沙地带北部局势快照</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:29:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/when-pita-made-of-animal-feed-is-your-best-case-scenario-life-in-northern-gaza/0000018d-89f5-d5e7-ad8d-ebf59baf0000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列不承诺停止援助抗议活动，布林肯取消了加沙过境访问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-cancels-gaza-crossing-visit-after-israel-doesnt-commit-to-stopping-aid-protests/0000018d-8a38-d443-a19f-feb9d3010000</link><description>美国国务卿本应亲自评估援助卡车从以色列前往加沙的通道，但由于担心抗议者出现，阻止援助卡车进入加沙，访问被取消</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-cancels-gaza-crossing-visit-after-israel-doesnt-commit-to-stopping-aid-protests/0000018d-8a38-d443-a19f-feb9d3010000</guid></item><item><title>由于航班将返回以色列，英国航空公司最大限度地减少了运营、飞机和机组人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/british-airways-minimizes-operations-plane-and-crew-as-flights-set-to-return-to-israel/0000018d-89be-d5e7-ad8d-ebbe48dc0000</link><description>在飞往以色列的途中，这架飞机将在塞浦路斯停留 45 分钟，进行机组人员换班，而乘客则留在机上。由于保险公司的条件，船员不会在以色列过夜</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 20:09:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/british-airways-minimizes-operations-plane-and-crew-as-flights-set-to-return-to-israel/0000018d-89be-d5e7-ad8d-ebbe48dc0000</guid></item><item><title>“无处可归”：《国土报》如何讲述加沙被毁的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/nowhere-to-return-to-how-haaretz-told-the-story-of-gazas-destruction/0000018d-89ea-d5e7-ad8d-ebea9a320000</link><description>“仅仅在图像旁边放置文字是不够的，”记者亚登·米凯利 (Yarden Michaeli) 谈到《国土报》对加沙地带大规模破坏的交互式视觉调查时说道。 “我们真的想让人们进入故事，以产生情感影响”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 19:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/nowhere-to-return-to-how-haaretz-told-the-story-of-gazas-destruction/0000018d-89ea-d5e7-ad8d-ebea9a320000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 125 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-125/0000018d-89d1-d5e7-ad8d-ebf1fac20000</link><description>布林肯表示，哈马斯对停火提议的回应“显然不可能”，但美国认为“这为达成协议创造了空间” ■ 哈马斯高级官员表示，内塔尼亚胡对哈马斯的答复表明总理打算在该地区寻求冲突 ■ 几名以色列人周四，一名真主党指挥官在黎巴嫩的火箭弹和导弹袭击中受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-125/0000018d-89d1-d5e7-ad8d-ebf1fac20000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列艺术家不再是以色列艺术家时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/this-week-in-culture-when-an-israeli-artist-is-not-an-israeli-artist/0000018d-892a-d9cc-a5cd-fdba9e700000</link><description>在本周的以色列文化综述中：艺术家兼电影制片人雅埃尔·巴塔纳 (Yael Bartana) 将代表德国参加今年的威尼斯双年展，海法取消了为两位失去亲人的父亲（一位是以色列人，另一位是巴勒斯坦人）举办的一本书的活动，特拉维夫博物馆仍在展出展览与赎罪日战争的斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:25:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/this-week-in-culture-when-an-israeli-artist-is-not-an-israeli-artist/0000018d-892a-d9cc-a5cd-fdba9e700000</guid></item><item><title>英国首相誓言打击亲巴勒斯坦集会上的“反犹太主义”和“暴力恐吓”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/britains-pm-vows-to-crack-down-on-antisemitism-at-pro-palestine-rallies/0000018d-897b-d443-a19f-fdfbabef0000</link><description>英国首相谴责伦敦抗议活动中表现出的“美化恐怖主义”，并发誓在英国反犹太主义率不断上升的情况下，警方将“阻止人们遮住脸来隐瞒身份”</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 17:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/britains-pm-vows-to-crack-down-on-antisemitism-at-pro-palestine-rallies/0000018d-897b-d443-a19f-fdfbabef0000</guid></item><item><title>纽约一家德鲁兹餐厅的墙上挂着一面以色列国旗。这时候麻烦就开始了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-druze-restaurant-in-ny-hung-an-israeli-flag-on-the-wall-thats-when-the-trouble-started/0000018d-880f-d0de-af8d-8c3fd87c0000</link><description>在曼哈顿的加扎拉餐厅，老板加扎拉哈拉比自豪地认为自己是以色列人，所用的橄榄油、香草和香料都是从“家乡”带来的。 10月7日之后的尖酸刻薄、破碎的玻璃和“自由巴勒斯坦”的涂鸦让她震惊，但她无意退缩</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 16:28:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-druze-restaurant-in-ny-hung-an-israeli-flag-on-the-wall-thats-when-the-trouble-started/0000018d-880f-d0de-af8d-8c3fd87c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列撤离人员所在的酒店报告了多起性暴力和家庭暴力案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/several-cases-of-sexual-and-domestic-violence-reported-at-hotels-housing-israeli-evacuees/0000018d-891d-d443-a19f-fd9d8bf20000</link><description>据警方称，已立案 116 起单独档案，其中包括针对未成年人和妇女的性侵犯案件。由于持续的战争，加沙和黎巴嫩边境地区共有约20万人流离失所</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:56:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/several-cases-of-sexual-and-domestic-violence-reported-at-hotels-housing-israeli-evacuees/0000018d-891d-d443-a19f-fd9d8bf20000</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙的生活和家园被摧毁，其高等教育也被摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-gazas-lives-and-homes-are-destroyed-so-is-its-higher-education/0000018d-8906-d970-a5ed-8976424f0000</link><description>加沙高等教育的破坏不是“附带损害”，而是以色列摧毁物质和精神基础设施政策的一部分</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:40:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-gazas-lives-and-homes-are-destroyed-so-is-its-higher-education/0000018d-8906-d970-a5ed-8976424f0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日袭击中丧生的以色列男子的家人告知加沙的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-man-killed-in-oct-7-attack-informed-body-held-in-gaza/0000018d-892e-d5e7-ad8d-ebaecd4b0000</link><description>贝埃里的梅尼·戈达尔和他的妻子在哈马斯袭击基布兹期间被杀。迄今为止，他的家人仍不知道他遗体的下落</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-man-killed-in-oct-7-attack-informed-body-held-in-gaza/0000018d-892e-d5e7-ad8d-ebaecd4b0000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫居民因在公寓内刺伤妇女而被起诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-resident-indicted-in-fatal-stabbing-of-woman-in-her-apartment/0000018d-887e-d061-abff-afff1b570000</link><description>犯罪嫌疑人是 33 岁的丹尼尔·马尔戈辛 (Daniel Margoshin)，他在夜间闯入受害人家中，刺伤她超过 31 刀。他放火烧毁了公寓和她的尸体，然后逃到耶路撒冷，在那里他试图袭击试图逮捕他的警察，结果被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:26:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-resident-indicted-in-fatal-stabbing-of-woman-in-her-apartment/0000018d-887e-d061-abff-afff1b570000</guid></item><item><title>阿根廷总统在访问被哈马斯蹂躏的以色列基布兹时将10月7日描述为“21世纪纳粹主义”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/argentine-president-describes-oct-7-as-21st-century-nazism-at-israeli-kibbutz/0000018d-891b-d061-abff-affbcf6c0000</link><description>极右翼总统米莱表示，“当我们听到 10 月 7 日所使用的方法时，这让我们想起了大屠杀的暴行”。他对犹太教着迷，并表示有兴趣皈依犹太教。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/argentine-president-describes-oct-7-as-21st-century-nazism-at-israeli-kibbutz/0000018d-891b-d061-abff-affbcf6c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列关于战争的艺术展不是“战争展览”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/an-israeli-art-exhibit-on-the-war-that-isnt-a-war-exhibition/0000018d-839d-d636-adef-cfff28230000</link><description>压抑的紧张感和克制的恐怖：特拉维夫英加画廊的展览受到加沙战争的影响，但以一种广泛的、存在主义的方式</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 14:12:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/an-israeli-art-exhibit-on-the-war-that-isnt-a-war-exhibition/0000018d-839d-d636-adef-cfff28230000</guid></item><item><title>加沙人逃离家园。他们无处可归 | “这令人震惊”：170 万巴勒斯坦人逃离了以色列对加沙的轰炸。他们的大部分房屋都被损坏或摧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-08/ty-article-static-ext/.premium/gazans-fled-their-homes-they-have-nowhere-to-return-to/0000018d-73f0-d4f1-a18d-f7f071190002</link><description>卫星揭示了加沙地带遭受的巨大破坏。以色列国防军的行动所创造的新现实将在数年内影响整个地区。这就是它的样子</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:59:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-08/ty-article-static-ext/.premium/gazans-fled-their-homes-they-have-nowhere-to-return-to/0000018d-73f0-d4f1-a18d-f7f071190002</guid></item><item><title>“我不得不离开以色列。 10月7日之后，我就不能再碰画笔了。”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-had-to-leave-israel-after-oct-7-i-wasnt-capable-of-touching-a-brush/0000018d-8888-dbf5-ab9d-cb8878a40000</link><description>10 月 7 日大屠杀发生几天后，以色列德鲁兹艺术家法特玛·沙南 (Fatma Shanan) 离开以色列前往欧洲。她解释了为什么她觉得有必要逃避阿拉伯以色列人不断要求谴责哈马斯袭击的要求</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 13:36:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-had-to-leave-israel-after-oct-7-i-wasnt-capable-of-touching-a-brush/0000018d-8888-dbf5-ab9d-cb8878a40000</guid></item></channel></rss>